{"title":"码头与船","authors":["陈咏华"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":8,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"码头与船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈咏华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上没有不散的筵席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可世上有长相厮守。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个，永远向往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个，默默等候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离，时在念中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合，相亲相求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是船与码头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿碰撞，只愿轻柔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶有碰撞，各自忍受。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有浪涛的轻浮，无度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相互解忧，消愁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有生活的丰满，欢快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相互分担，接收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎迎送送，都为了顺风顺流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起起伏伏，都扛重任肩头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远近近，从未将相思轻丢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相依相偎，是为了前程锦绣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相离相别呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清谁走谁留。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}